Global Aerospace and Defense Devices Market Insights
Aerospace and Defense Devices Market size was valued at USD 90 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 120 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Aerospace and Defense Devices Market Overview
The global aerospace and defense devices market has been steadily growing, driven by increased demand for advanced technology and defense innovations. In 2023, the market was valued at USD 1.1 trillion and is projected to reach USD 1.6 trillion by 2030, expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.6% from 2024 to 2030. This growth is attributed to rising geopolitical tensions, technological advancements, and the need for modernized defense systems. The aerospace segment is seeing increased investments in space exploration and satellite technologies, while the defense sector focuses on unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), military systems, and defense electronics.

